    #cooking.face
      .about_cooking_wide
        .about_cooking_half_overlay
          %p
            Anyone who knows me can attest to my passion for food.
          %p
            After reading Anthony Bordain's
            = link_to "'Kitchen Confidential'", 'http://www.amazon.com/Kitchen-Confidential-Anthony-Bourdain/dp/1408845040/ref=sr_1_3?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1404002819&sr=1-3&keywords=kitchen+confidential+by+anthony+bourdain', :target => '_blank'
            and
            = link_to "'Heat'", 'http://www.amazon.com/Heat-Adventures-Pasta-Maker-Apprentice-Dante-Quoting/dp/1400034477/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1404002756&sr=1-1&keywords=heat+bill+buford', :target => '_blank'
            by Bill Buford, I was inspired to take a stab at being a chef myself.
          %p
            From
            %span.large_print
              2006
            until
            %span.large_print
              2008
            &dash; under the tutelage of chef Daniel Parilla &dash; I was inducted into the super-intense, never-boring under-world of the professional kitchen by working my way up the line at
            = link_to '5Ninth,', 'http://nymag.com/nymetro/food/reviews/restaurant/9564/', :target => '_blank'
            a distinguished restaurant in New York City's Meatpacking District.

    #radio.face
      .about_radio_wide
        .about_radio_half_overlay
          %p
            I spent the years between
            %span.large_print
              2008
            &amp;
            %span.large_print
              2012
            working at
            = link_to 'WNYC / New York Public Radio.', 'http://www.wnyc.org', :target => '_blank'

          %p
            I got my foot in the door interning at
            = link_to 'RadioLab', 'http://www.radiolab.org', :target => '_blank'
            where I assisted in the production of its 5th season. Later, I would compose music for some of the show's live events.

          %p
            I held my first staff position at
            = link_to 'The Takeaway', 'http://www.thetakeaway.org', :target => '_blank'
            &dash; a nationally aired morning drive news program hosted by the inimitable
            = link_to 'John Hockenberry', 'http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Hockenberry', :target => '_blank'
            &dash; where I spent my days pitching news story ideas and interviewing political, academic and cultural figures of international renown in order to script and produce
            = link_to 'radio segments', 'http://www.thetakeaway.org/people/hsi-chang-lin/', :target => '_blank'
            for air the following morning.

          %p
            On the days that I filled in as the show's managing producer I was responsible for four hours of editorial content, organizing stories under tight deadlines.

          %p
            Along the way I filed stories for
            = link_to 'Studio 360,', 'http://www.studio360.org', :target => '_blank'
            and sat as judge on an American Idol-esque panel for the radio station's city-wide music competetion
            = link_to 'The Battle of the Borroughs', 'http://www.thegreenespace.org/series/battle-boroughs-2014/', :target => '_blank'
            on several occasions.
